<subSubSection id="C326E0F8A657220D38EB38D30E502B97" pageId="18" pageNumber="101" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B83B373A657220D38EB38D30A982C8B" blockId="18.[189,416,931,958]" box="[189,416,931,958]" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">
<emphasis id="B9486F61A657220D38EB38D30A0E2C88" bold="true" box="[189,310,931,957]" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Diagnosis</emphasis>
(female)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B83B373A657220D38EB38A30E502B97" blockId="18.[188,1399,979,1186]" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">
Body length 
<quantity id="4CC41E96A657220D390D38A30AD62CD8" box="[347,494,979,1006]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.15" metricValueMax="3.5" metricValueMin="2.8" pageId="18" pageNumber="101" unit="mm" value="3.15" valueMax="3.5" valueMin="2.8">2.8–3.5 mm</quantity>
; antenna as long as body, F15 length 2.0 × its width (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D3CD338A30FCD2CD8" box="[1157,1269,979,1005]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10A</figureCitation>
); in dorsal view, head width 1.8 × its length (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D3A0A388709F22B24" box="[604,714,1015,1041]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10B</figureCitation>
); anteromesoscutum rugulose; mesoscutellar disc weakly rugulose (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D39633F6B0A992B00" box="[309,417,1051,1077]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10C</figureCitation>
); vein R1 as long as pterostigma half; 1 
<superScript id="7C491E3BA657220D3B253F6B08462B1C" attach="left" box="[883,894,1051,1065]" fontSize="6" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">st</superScript>
discal cell length 1.2–1.3 × its width; vein 1CUb 2.0 × as long as vein 1CUa (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D3A073F4F09862B6C" box="[593,702,1087,1113]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10D</figureCitation>
); T1 length 2.0 × its maximum width, T1 smooth, shiny and parallel- to sub-parallel-sided (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D3A7B3F1309A02B4B" box="[557,664,1123,1150]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10F</figureCitation>
). Colour: body black; antenna and metatarsus brown; tegula, tergites and legs reddish yellow to yellow; basal one third of pterostigma with a yellow spot (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A657220D3D543FF80E622B97" box="[1282,1370,1160,1186]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="19.[189,232,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-44@19.[189,1398,614,1889]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="Fig. 10. Microplitis rufiventris Kokujev, 1914, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0057. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Fore wing. E. Hind wing. F. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690350" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690350/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="101">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
